Name: Highway Thru Hell
Title: Fly Or Fall
Desc: Greg takes charge on his biggest recovery; Gord hustles to open the Coq's steepest stretch.
LongDescription: Team Reliable is in foggy chaos; Ken turns an off-road recovery into a joyride; Greg takes charge on his biggest recovery without the boss; Gord hustles to open the Coq's steepest stretch.
